data.description: **PRICE ADJUSTMENT in CLOVER ISD** Looking for a home in a family friendly neighborhood?  Sit on your rocking chair front porch and enjoy your morning coffee or afternoon tea while you wait for the kiddos to come off the school bus.  This beauty in Mill Creek Falls is what you've been looking for. This 4 bedroom 2 bath ranch style home features vaulted ceilings, an open living space with LVP flooring, mudroom/laundry room, 2 car garage with extended driveway for plenty of parking & dedicated garage access.  From the primary suite, you will enjoy dedicated access to enjoy your back patio, maple and fruit trees in your fully fenced backyard.   Nice split home living with master and en-suite to one side of the home and remaining 3 beds and bath on opposite side. You'll love the community amenities that include a community center and pool, walking trails, tennis courts, disc golf, community pond and picnic areas.  All appliances will remain ... including the washer and dryer.
